Market Segmentation: 
The label adhesive market is segmented on the basis of technology, substrate type, process and application. The growth amongst the different segments helps you in attaining the knowledge related to the different growth factors expected to be prevalent throughout the market and formulate different strategies to help identify core application areas and the difference in your target markets.
Based on technology, the label adhesive market is segmented into water based, hot melt based and solvent based others.
On the basis of substrate type, the label adhesive market is segmented into pet bottle, metal container, glass bottle, polyolefin bottle and others.
Based on process, the label adhesive market is segmented into pressure sensitive adhesive, glue applied, In-mold and others.
The label adhesive market is also segmented on the basis of application into permanent adhesives, peelable adhesives, freezer adhesive and high temperature adhesive.
